Where is it?

589
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,680
It was just here.

590
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,040
Wanfu has it.

591
00:31:17,600 --> 00:31:18,640
Where is the sword?

592
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,920
In the bundle.

593
00:31:21,600 --> 00:31:22,720
Boatman, hurry up.

594
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:23,960
If we're late,

595
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,400
I'll miss the Meiyun.

596
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,940
Don't worry, you'll definitely make it.

597
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:28,840
I'm telling you,

598
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:30,300
I won't pay you if I miss it.

599
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:32,440
Okay, don't worry.

600
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:57,560
Airplanes!

601
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:15,200
Japanese planes!

602
00:32:15,560 --> 00:32:16,120
Oh no!

603
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:17,120
Japanese planes!

604
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:18,480
Japanese planes!

605
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:19,880
Row faster!

606
00:32:21,360 --> 00:32:22,240
Master, don't fall.

607
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:23,280
I'm fine, you...

608
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,120
Master!

609
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,360
I hope they don't bomb us.

610
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:26,960
The boats over there seem to have been bombed.

611
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:27,480
Master!

612
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,240
Slow down.

613
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,280
The Meiyun.

614
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,720
Ma'am, be careful.

615
00:32:44,120 --> 00:32:44,760
Father,

616
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:46,290
Wanfu is on the boat.

617
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,120
Wanfu!

618
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:47,960
Wanfu! Yes!

619
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:55,920
Ma'am, there's a small boat over there.

620
00:32:55,920 --> 00:32:57,560
There's someone on it. Look,

621
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:00,080
it's rowing this way.

622
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,240
Is that Wanfu?

623
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:03,720
Wanfu! Wanfu!

624
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:04,920
It's Wanfu, Mrs. Liu.

625
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:06,180
Father, that's Wanfu.

626
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:07,440
It's Wanfu! Wanfu is on the boat!

627
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:08,560
Wanfu!

628
00:33:57,960 --> 00:34:01,840
Good.

629
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:24,810
I'm telling you.

630
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:25,520
Today,

631
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,840
anyone can leave,

632
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:27,960
but not you.

633
00:34:28,239 --> 00:34:29,600
Today you are staying here,

634
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:30,960
to watch us die,

635
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:31,960
to watch me die.

636
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:41,480
Congratulations to the newlyweds.

637
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:43,480
Congratulations to the newlyweds.

638
00:34:47,719 --> 00:34:48,960
Zhang Yunkui.

639
00:34:49,520 --> 00:34:50,449
I'm telling you.

640
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,810
Anyone can leave today,

641
00:34:52,120 --> 00:34:53,600
except you.

642
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:54,960
Stay here

643
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:57,560
and see how I cook.

644
00:34:58,000 --> 00:35:00,480
Okay, okay.

645
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:00,960
Okay.

646
00:36:24,120 --> 00:36:25,000
Kong Erbao,

647
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:26,960
where did you send the sword?

648
00:36:28,240 --> 00:36:29,480
I'm telling you.

649
00:36:30,200 --> 00:36:31,840
Anyone can leave except you.

650
00:36:32,520 --> 00:36:33,040
I want you to see

651
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:35,280
exactly how we die.

652
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:22,810
Kick him. Kick him to death.

653
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:25,320
You're awake.

654
00:37:26,560 --> 00:37:27,080
Wanfu.

655
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:30,000
You're awake.

656
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:42,240
Wanfu, Wanfu.

657
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,560
Where am I?

658
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,640
Am I in the underworld?

659
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:54,280
You are here too.

660
00:37:55,000 --> 00:37:55,480
You...

661
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,840
Bite your tongue.

662
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,120
You are alive.

663
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:00,770
Don't you remember?

664
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:03,840
Meiyun ship was bombed.

665
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:06,920
Didn't you get on a small boat?

666
00:38:07,920 --> 00:38:09,780
We saw you fall into the water too.

667
00:38:10,560 --> 00:38:11,640
But fortunately,

668
00:38:11,640 --> 00:38:13,560
your boat was close to us.

669
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:15,360
So the crew on board

670
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,520
saved you.

671
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:21,080
Yes, I got on the small boat.

672
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:23,560
Yes, I got on the small boat

673
00:38:24,520 --> 00:38:26,600
just to deliver the sword to you.

674
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:29,880
Where is the sword?

675
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,890
Where is the bag?

676
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,340
Where is the sword?

677
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:35,240
Where is the sword?

678
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:36,500
They are all kept safe.

679
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:37,720
They're not lost.

680
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:39,040
Don't worry.

681
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:45,280
My... where is my wallet?

682
00:38:46,560 --> 00:38:47,680
Your clothes have been washed.

683
00:38:47,680 --> 00:38:49,040
Your things are kept over there.

684
00:38:49,040 --> 00:38:50,170
Nothing is missing.

685
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:55,880
Come, lie down.

686
00:38:58,480 --> 00:38:59,880
Get him something to eat.

687
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:02,000
Wanfu.

688
00:39:02,720 --> 00:39:04,640
We are really destined to meet.

689
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,540
You see, you were entrusted by Yunkui

690
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:10,560
to deliver the sword to Nanjing,

691
00:39:10,960 --> 00:39:12,280
and we met.

692
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:14,980
This time, you delivered the sword again

693
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:17,260
and escaped the disaster of Meiyun ship.

694
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:18,360
This shows

695
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:21,240
that God is blessing you in the dark.

696
00:39:21,680 --> 00:39:22,080
Right?

697
00:39:22,080 --> 00:39:23,120
Oh no.

698
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,200
Oh no.

699
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:26,000
What's wrong?

700
00:39:26,080 --> 00:39:27,760
Meiyun ship is gone.

701
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:30,240
How can I go to Wuhan?

702
00:39:33,040 --> 00:39:34,240
Wanfu,

703
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:37,960
you are on the Ophelia now.

704
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:40,280
You will go to Shanghai with us.

705
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:42,600
To Shanghai?

706
00:39:43,680 --> 00:39:45,880
The ferry ticket from Shanghai to Wuhan is more expensive.

707
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:47,440
I can't afford it.

708
00:39:48,520 --> 00:39:49,440
What time is it now?

709
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:50,920
And you are still thinking about the ferry ticket?

710
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:52,040
Is life more important,

711
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:52,960
or the ticket?

712
00:39:54,640 --> 00:39:55,600
Wanfu,

713
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:57,940
you are a loyal and righteous man.

714
00:39:58,160 --> 00:40:00,560
Our Zhang family will never treat you unfairly.

715
00:40:00,560 --> 00:40:02,040
After we arrive in Shanghai

716
00:40:02,040 --> 00:40:03,440
and settle down,

717
00:40:03,720 --> 00:40:06,520
we will pay for your ferry ticket to Wuhan.

718
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:09,360
Really?

719
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:13,760
Master,

720
00:40:14,640 --> 00:40:15,960
you keep your word.

721
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:17,640
With what you said,

722
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,880
I feel much more at ease.

723
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,120
Come, sit up.

724
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:23,920
Come.

725
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:28,040
Come.

726
00:40:29,160 --> 00:40:30,080
Drink some sugar water first.

727
00:40:30,080 --> 00:40:30,680
It's hot.

728
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:36,480
Don't let him drink anymore.

729
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:38,540
His stomach is already full of water.

730
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:40,760
Honestly,

731
00:40:42,520 --> 00:40:43,400
Madam,

732
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:45,440
I'm hungry.

733
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:48,040
Mrs. Liu,

734
00:40:48,640 --> 00:40:50,040
get him something to eat.

735
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:08,760
Another one threw up, look.

736
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:09,400
Madam.

737
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:24,480
Chivalrous and courageous.
